{"type": "article", "id": 36983, "title": "让鸡蛋“坐”进船里，你就能有美味的早餐｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-01-18T22:59:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 15539, "name": "maison 203"}, {"id": 30564, "name": "OTOTO"}, {"id": 36875, "name": "DesignLibero"}, {"id": 36876, "name": "Odo Fioravanit"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 174, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170118230627u2EYGsrzytohdxfe.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #323333} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Eggondola by OTOTO</h3><p>下次早餐时做鸡蛋，可以把千篇一律的小碗换成这艘蓝色的贡多拉了。Eggondola 是以色列设计工作室 OTOTO 的最新产品，由硅胶制成。让鸡蛋“坐”进船里，只要几分钟就能完成一个美味的水煮蛋。它将于 2 月正式销售，你可以通过<a href=\"http://www.ototodesign.com/collections/all-products/products/eggondola-egg-poacher\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>预定，售价为 14 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118230648PowB2izQfTdb4qNO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675676\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118230648WyQDvNCY5IqfdiJu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118230648jNRa1qeWwsV0E4I6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Shovava by Roza Khamitova </h3><p>用可以穿的艺术品来形容澳大利亚设计师 Roza Khamitova 创立的服饰品牌 Shovava 似乎再合适不过了。哈萨克斯坦裔的 Khamitova 在一次丛林旅行中得到了启发，她决定从大自然中汲取灵感，将每天都能碰到的各种鸟类的翅膀描绘在披肩上。每一款披肩都是由她亲手绘制，随后在印度采用数码喷绘制作而成。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/Shovava/\" rel=\"nofollow\">网店链接</a>，售价从 48 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118230710vZtCOrE314fURxoz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.620000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118230710tpPy8jEQLHqWCAg0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.620000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118230710LGlykK2R6iQs73Iz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.620000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118230710tnNDXpUdFwW0rjlC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.620000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>MagNeo by Branch</h3><p>苹果推出的新款 MacBook Pro 取消了独特而且便捷的 Magsafe 磁性电源接口，改成了 USB-C 的接头。对于用惯了磁性连接线的用户来说，如果想要继续用上之前的方法，就只能购买配件商推出的产品，而它们大多也仅限于为笔记本充电。最近来自美国的设计团队 Branch 就推出了一款集磁性接口、充电和数据传输等功能的适配器 MagNeo，适用于所有拥有 USB-C 接头的设备，而且无论正反插入都能正常工作。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/branchusb/magneo-first-true-usb-c-magnetic-adapter\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 35 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118230814JEZcl2pgLBY9f0Iq.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118230814IwJHvB1nXT6LOdPW.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.614583\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118230814ztnRYa2JVq6T1pWy.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.644118\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118230814BcGiUuAns3TQ2HLX.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.711765\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118230812TG6UWwapOEXIxJPZ.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Boris by DesignLibero</h3><p>这只来自意大利设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.designlibero.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">DesignLibero</a> 的喵星人名叫 Boris，喜欢呆在床或是沙发边上，对阅读有着浓厚的兴趣。和走极简路线力求融入室内环境的杂志架不同，你很难无视 Boris 的存在感。它由橙色粉末喷涂的金属管弯曲而成，看起来就像是一只虎斑猫。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701182307561tENnmePJuDhjw4L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701182307563HT2Yq5IGLWKh4Zz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118230756lBpmI7FxHh0LUT4z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118230756zrlshiVS1oOMHWY2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Bern clutch by Odo Fioravanit</h3><p>在即将于本周开幕的法国家具博览会上，意大利 3D 打印首饰品牌 <a href=\"http://www.maison203.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Maison 203</a> 准备展出由设计师 <a href=\"http://www.fioravanti.eu/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Odo Fioravanit</a> 为旗下 Bern 系列设计的一款手拿包。这个系列得名自瑞士首都伯尔尼，手拿包的表面和此前推出的首饰上的纹路一样，都借鉴了城区内蜿蜒曲折而平行的道路系统。虽然这些包都是用烧结尼龙制成的，但独特的结构赋予了它们一种金属感，好像是小型的雕塑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118230741Kfhglj3Y5vV24mDP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701182307417KNEV5g1LyZRmcjJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.178750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118230741SjUzODWusVEPh5R2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.648750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Measuring Noodles Bag by Zhao Bingcong et al.</h3><p>煮面时不确定要下多少的量是不少人都经历过的难题，为了减少这一困扰，江西财经大学的四位学生设计了一款带度量标尺的面条包装。标尺和包装的开口处于同一位置，上面标记了一到三人份这三个不同的刻度，撕开包装后只需要将橡胶制的小夹子拖动到对应的位置，倒出来的面条就刚刚好够吃不会浪费或是太少了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170118230840Idq0APugnT28M1Da.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750366\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}